<geoCoordinate id="171DEDC957B9FE2692156F6257A4115A" degrees="120" direction="east" minutes="57" orientation="longitude" precision="1" seconds="26.4" value="120.95733">120°57'26.4&quot;E</geoCoordinate>
, 670 m asl., on dead angiosperm trunk, 20 Aug 2020, leg. C.L. Wei, WEI 20-166 (holotype, TNM F34448). GenBank: ITS = MW580922; 28S = MW580924.
</paragraph>
<caption id="9EF6D10605A722B7250044CAE0403253" doi="10.3897/mycokeys.90.84562.figure3" httpUri="https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/690445" pageId="0" pageNumber="19" start="Figure 3" startId="F3">
